@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pgbewy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v1 + 0.43 * v1 + 0.12)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.01)) / wp.abs((tmp + 0.99 * v2 + 0.99)))
    v0 = 0.13
    v0 = (v2 - wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.06)))
    v2 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.45 - v0 + 0.71) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.12)))
    v0 = 0.94
    data[tid] = v0
